overview: The user's intent is to complete the development of a Sleep
  Questionnaire Application by implementing a database for response storage and
  an admin dashboard for data access, as outlined in their SOW. I performed an
  initial evaluation of the existing codebase, which revealed that while the
  questionnaire logic and PDF generation were largely in place, the database for
  responses, data retrieval (CSV export), and an admin dashboard with
  authentication were missing. To ensure the plan aligns with the user's
  preferences, I asked for clarification on the desired authentication
  complexity for the dashboard and to resolve a discrepancy in the demographic
  data fields specified in the SOW versus what's currently in the form. This
  will allow for a tailored and efficient implementation plan.
